Ms. Schapiro currently serves as an Independent Director of General Electric Corporation, Vice Chairman of the Advisory Board of Promontory Financial Group Network and a board member of The London Stock Exchange Group. Ms. Schapiro previously served as the 29th Chairman of the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission from January 2009 through December 2012, Chief Executive Officer of FINRA, Chairman of the CFTC, and Commissioner of the SEC.




